<subSubSection id="14936530FF9388652BB1E58CC5F8F964" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="5C3636BBFF9388652BB1E58CC5F8F964" blockId="21.[158,796,1699,1774]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis id="6EFDEAA9FF9388652BB1E58CC4C3F932" box="[158,239,1699,1720]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Diagnosis</emphasis>
: Shell small to medium-sized (
<emphasis id="6EFDEAA9FF938865293EE58CC608F932" box="[529,548,1699,1720]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">&lt;</emphasis>
<quantity id="9B719B5EFF938865290BE58CC645F933" box="[548,617,1699,1721]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" unit="mm" value="50.0">50 mm</quantity>
), solid; axial sculpture weak to obsolete; spiral sculpture of irregular punctate groves; subsutural band weakly defined.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
